init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: These individuals are known as "Mana-users" and are the only ones capable of wielding magic.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Mana-users are now the last hope of humanity.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Mana-users are divided into two factions: the Light and the Dark.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Light Mana-users are the ones who wish to use their power to help humanity.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Light Mana-users must now band together to stop him before it is too late.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Light Mana-users were losing the battle.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The ancient ally was a being of immense power and knowledge.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was known as the "First Light" and was the first of the Mana-users.
